tweet: This week I’ve been working to convince my Senate colleagues that a lapse in NFIP would be a disservice to families across the country, & especially for us in Louisiana. I’m glad that last night the Senate voted to pass my bill to extend NFIP for 6 months https://bit.ly/2DPT3Ns
